# CTcl2txt - refgen configuration spec for CTcl input, plain-text output
#
# Copyright 1998 Wind River Systems, Inc.
#
# modification history
# --------------------
# 01a,16jul98,rhp  Initial check-in

IN  CTcl                        # process C source files that define Tcl procs
OUT Txt                         # output plain text

LIBIX  {LIBS.txt Libraries}         # Library index, and how to refer to it
ROUTIX {PROCS.txt {Tcl Procedures}} # Routine index, and how to refer to it

ROUTINES yes                    # Print subroutines by default?
